      • fireTreeStructureChanged

        private void fireTreeStructureChanged​(Object source,
                                      Object[] path,
                                      int[] childIndices,
                                      Object... children)
        Notify all listeners that have registered interest in 'tree structure changed' event. The event instance is lazily created using the parameters passed into the fire method.
        Parameters:
        source - The Object responsible for generating the event.
        path - An array of Object identifying the path to the parent of the modified items.
        childIndices - An array of int that specifies the index values of the removed items.
        children - An array of Object containing the inserted, removed, or changed objects.
        See Also:
        EventListenerList
